      "description": "Available now is a breathtaking 2021 Porsche 718 Cayman, finished in timeless GT Silver Metallic. This vehicle is the definition of 'mint' condition, having been preserved in a climate-controlled environment and driven only on fair-weather weekends. The exterior paint is deep, glossy, and entirely free of stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks, thanks to a full-body paint protection film (PPF) and professional ceramic coating. The staggered 20-inch Carrera S wheels are immaculate with no curb rash, wrapped in the original Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires with ample tread. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the black leather sport seats show zero bolster wear, the steering wheel retains its factory matte finish, and the carpets have been protected by weather-tech liners since delivery. Every electronic feature, from the Bose Surround Sound to the Porsche Communication Management system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with all maintenance performed exclusively at authorized Porsche centers\u2014full service records are included. This is a rare opportunity to own",
